# Upstream Tessera REST API origin (the running engine — see apps/server). SERVER-ONLY: the browser
# never talks to it directly (ADR-0048). The dashboard calls a same-origin proxy (/api/tessera) that
# attaches the bearer token from an httpOnly session cookie and forwards to this origin.
# Defaults to the Local profile address when unset.
TESSERA_API_URL=http://localhost:3000
